QUO - Within The Backrooms

'QUO - Within The Backrooms' is a first-person dystopian-horror sci fi-liminal adventure inspired by Backrooms. In this mission you are QUO, an autonomous robot explorer. Trace, probe and delve into an unexplored reality full of enigmas and dangers. Now it's your turn.
